{"tid":572003,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"香港航空新航線 2018","createTime":"2018-02-25T08:07:50.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-28T02:51:40.000Z","uid":150989,"like":22,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":25,"replies":[{"pid":"67a72d29f50b7f3b6f27187c7a48b9ee8df1380d","tid":572003,"uid":150989,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-25T08:07:51.000Z","msg":"1月11日起，加密沖繩航線班次（逢週二、四、五、六），令其每周航班數目增至十八班<br />\n<br />\n1月16日起，復辦每週三班往來香港至馬爾代夫直航服務，採用空中巴士A330-300客機營運。<br />\n<br />\n3月25日起，開通每週四班往來香港至三藩市的直航服務，以全新空中巴士A350-900客機營運。<br />\n<br />\n並將於稍後陸續開辦來往香港至<span style=\"color: red;\">馬尼拉</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 、 莫斯科-伏努科沃 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />、德國-柏林、<span style=\"color: blue;\">倫敦-希斯路</span> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 、倫敦-格域機場、紐約-甘迺迪及多倫多航線。"},{"pid":"31507ca0ce7286e66ac08a01a570b092e3bd50a7","tid":572003,"uid":55732,"like":26,"dislike":1,"score":25,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-26T05:04:30.000Z","msg":"呢間嘢開到上月球都唔會搭佢啦"},{"pid":"d45667001016d096d82b267c7ca4b6c61d55cfd7","tid":572003,"uid":116330,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-26T05:08:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://c1.staticflickr.com/5/4043/4299913941_95f2074d43.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fc1.staticflickr.com%2F5%2F4043%2F4299913941_95f2074d43.jpg&h=7b0a09e8&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"3b258643e6a4b2f307fe7467400094bafc2dc6bf","tid":572003,"uid":31841,"like":3,"dislike":25,"score":-22,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-26T05:12:46.000Z","msg":"快D開Long haul,蚀死佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3b5660ac96d2807d2a043e99f0006d108db652dc","tid":572003,"uid":37661,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-26T05:29:13.000Z","msg":"莫斯科-伏努科沃<br />\n<br />